2 )Question Title: Meter Conversion Unit

Question Description:

Develop a Java program to convert Meter between Centimeter and Kilometer. 
The Meter class includes a double value attribute, along with methods to perform conversions. 
Subclasses Centimeter and Kilometer extend Meter. In the Main class, users input a meter value, 
and the program converts and displays the value in the opposite unit.

Boilerplate Code:

import java.util.Scanner; class Meter { double value; public Meter(double value) 
{ this.value = value; } } class Centimeter extends Meter { //fill code } 
class Kilometer extends Meter { //fill code } } public class Main { 
public static void main(String[] args) { //fill your code here } }

Sample Input1:

Kilometer 200

Sample Output1:

Converted Unit :0.2 km

